name: Intoxication
description:
Half of the 16 oz glass of vodka mixed with candy was consumed within 2 minutes. The drink was so sweet and smooth you would had thought it was juice. However, the strength of the liquor mixed in the drink was hugely underestimated. As a result, the Big Shot transcend me to Jolly Paradise. The only thing left to consume was the vodka-infused blue raspberry gummy bears that patiently waited at the top to further my intoxication state. This visual is what I saw after every second that passed by.

Optional X/6 'Candy Martini Bar Collection.' 

Collectors must collect 6/6 different art pieces of the Candy Martini Bar Collection to get the 'Big Shot' NFT transferred to them at no cost.

This piece is optional to collect but will count towards the 6/6 (as 1/6) different art pieces of the Candy Martini Bar Collection to get the 'Big Shot' NFT transferred at no cost. The collector still needs to collect 2/6-6/6 to be eligible for the 'The Big Shot' reward.
